{"tid":1599493,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【每日10秒】迫TVB賣屎忽，每日洗版任務 - 恒基嘅千色店","createTime":"2019-09-28T04:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:03:32.000Z","uid":267969,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"0842f6bb2ab7c7cb64e4faedb7fe09fdb662057f","tid":1599493,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:19:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無綫怕黃絲廣告公司狙擊<br />\n破天荒取消11.8台慶亮燈及節目巡禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n汁：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mko71P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mko71P&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a18ff2bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2mko71P</a><br />\nTVB係品牌負資產，廣告公司都唔撐！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">幾日後</span></span>開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">年底</span></span>啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong> <br />\n<br />\n千色母公司恒基支持送中、撐特首、撐警、抹黑民研<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲喺CCTVB賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，梗係冇人買要減價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過減價係冇用架，你一日唔撤回廣告，我地一日都會抵制！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70909170_461173714739483_2256577908967473152_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQnlIXdqOx8v3-1eq8YcuPpFO2R-Tfww1CgG6evwl-6dQwsZRbh9bIwPozouKfBFjrM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=51982f94b3927835b2e52238a56f1cd2&amp;oe=5E38951A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70909170_461173714739483_2256577908967473152_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQnlIXdqOx8v3-1eq8YcuPpFO2R-Tfww1CgG6evwl-6dQwsZRbh9bIwPozouKfBFjrM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D51982f94b3927835b2e52238a56f1cd2%26oe%3D5E38951A&h=393f182d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n是日精選@28 Sep 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>千色店</strong></span></span> <strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/citistorehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcitistorehk%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=fba8fab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/citistorehk/</a></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請用幾秒</span></strong>去派嬲、留言、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得?</span></strong>  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌只開行動post，順便follow埋<br />\n<br />\n <strong>※留言template，二擇其一，歡迎創意留言。</strong> <br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定唔去千色店直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家用呢幅圖留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbc